      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman is a true collector\u2019s specimen, maintained with obsessive care and presented in showroom state. The exterior is finished in a flawless Guards Red, protected by a professional ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like shine with absolutely no stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the black leather interior remains pristine; the seat bolsters show zero signs of entry wear, and the cabin retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, having been serviced exclusively at authorized Porsche centers with a comprehensive maintenance log included. It has been stored strictly in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover and has never been driven in inclement weather. Every electronic component, button, and mechanical system functions perfectly. This vehicle offers the rare chance to own a modern performance icon that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
